1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. Nc3 Be7 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bf4 c6 7. Qc2 g6 8. e3 Bf5 9. Bd3 Bxd3 10. Qxd3 Nbd7 11. h3 Nf8 12. g4!? { White commits to going queenside and launching a kingside attack. } 12... Ne6 { [%cal Gf4e5] } 13. Bg3 (13. Be5!? { [%cal Ge5h8] } 13... O-O $10) 13... Qa5 14. Nd2 { [%cal Gd2e4,Gf6e4] } 14... O-O 15. O-O-O?! (15. Kf1 { It's not too late to simply claim g4 was to gain space. } { [%cal Gf1g2] }) 15... Bb4 (15... Rfc8! 16. Kb1 b5 17. Rc1 b4 18. Nb3! Qd8 19. Na4 Ne4 { If the bishop were better placed on e5, this would be playable for white. } { [%csl Gg3] }) 16. Kb1 Bxc3 17. Qxc3 Qxc3 18. bxc3 { No longer a game of attacking opposite sides' kings. } { [%cal Gb1b7] } 18... Ne4? (18... Rac8! 19. f3 c5 $15) (18... Ng5? 19. f3! { [%csl Ge4][%cal Gf3e4] } 19... Rfe8 20. Kb2! { Black has nothing here. } 20... Rxe3?? 21. Bf4 $18) 19. Nxe4 dxe4 { Black should not have traded his great knight for white's bad knight. } 20. Kc2 $10 Rad8 21. a4 (21. Rb1 Rd7 22. Rb2) 21... f5! 22. gxf5?! Rxf5 { [%cal Gf5f2] } 23. c4 Rd7 24. Kc3 Ng7 { [%cal Gg7h5,Gh5g3,Gf5f2] } 25. Rd2 Kf7 26. Bb8 b6 27. Ra2 { [%cal Ga4a5] } 27... Ra5 28. Be5?! (28. f3!! exf3 29. Rf1 Rf5 30. e4 $16 { [%cal Ge4e5,Ge5e6,Ge6e7,Ge7e8] }) 28... Nf5 29. Rg1 h5 { [%csl Gg4] } (29... Nh4 30. Rg4 { [%csl Gg4] } 30... Nf3 31. Rxe4 $18) 30. Bf4? (30. Kb3 Nh4 31. Bf4 Nf3 32. Rg2 a6 $17 { [%cal Gb6b5] }) (30. Rf1 Nh4 31. f4! { White's pieces need to breathe! }) (30. Bg3 g5! 31. Rg2 Kg6 32. Rg1 Nxg3 33. fxg3 (33. Rxg3 Rf7 $17) 33... Rf7 $17) 30... Nh4 { [%cal Gh4f3] } 31. Rg5 Rxg5 32. Bxg5 Nf3 33. h4 (33. Bf4? g5! 34. Bb8 Ng1 $17 { [%cal Gg1h3] }) 33... Nxg5 34. hxg5 Ke6 35. a5 h4 { Passed h pawn is too strong } 36. Ra1 (36. axb6 axb6 37. Ra1 h3 38. Rh1 Rh7 39. Rh2 Kf5 40. Kb4 Kxg5 41. c5 bxc5+? (41... b5! 42. d5 cxd5 43. Kxb5 Kh4?? (43... Kf6! 44. c6 Ke5 $19) 44. c6 g5 45. Kc5 g4 46. Kxd5 g3 47. fxg3+ Kxg3 48. Rh1 Kg2 49. Rc1 h2 50. Kxe4 h1=Q 51. Rxh1 Kxh1 52. Kd5 $10) 42. Kxc5 Kf6!! 43. Kxc6 g5 44. d5 g4 45. d6 Ke6 46. Kc5 Rd7 $19) 36... bxa5 37. Kd2 h3 38. Ke2 h2 39. f3 Rh7 40. Rh1 exf3+ 41. Kxf3 a4 $19 0-1


