g6 29. Ne7+ Bxe7 30. fxe7 { [%cal Gb5a4] } 30... b4 { Desperation - trying to distract the bishop from the long diagonal. } 31. Bxb4 Qxa4 32. Bc3 { [%cal Gc3h8] } 32... Rxe7 33. Qh6 Ne5 34. Qg5?? (34. Rd6 a6 35. Rxg6+ fxg6 36. Bxe5 Rxe5 37. Qxg6+ Kh8 38. Rf7 $18) 34... Qe8?? (34... Rae8 35. Rd8 Re6! { Missed in the game. } 36. Rxe8+ (36. Bxe5 Rxe5 { [%cal Gd8e8,Ge5e8,Ga4e8] } 37. Qxe5 Rxd8 $17) (36. h4 Rxd8 37. Qxd8+ { [%cal Gg8g7] } 37... Kg7 (37... Qe8 38. Qg5 $15 { [%cal Gg2h3,Ge6e7] }) 38. Bxe5+ Rxe5 39. Qf6+ { [%cal Gf6e5,Gf6f7] }) 36... Qxe8 $10) 35. Rf4 Rc8 36. Rh4 Rxc3? 37. Qh6?? (37. Qf6! $18 { Black saw this as soon as he moved. White completely missed it... }) 37... f6? (37... f5! $10) 38. bxc3 Rg7? (38... Kf7 39. Rd6 Qg8 $16) 39. Rd8! Qxd8 40. Qh8+ Kf7 41. Qxd8 g5 42. Rh6 $18 { Black resigned. } 1-0


